dct_title_s: Ljubljana city map of Ljubljana : mestna karta | city map | 1:15 000
dct_description_sm: City street map showing buildings, generalized land use, and local transit routes. Relief shown by shading and spot heights. Title from cover. UTM grid. Notes, street index, city-center map, detailed diagrammatic map of LPP local transit routes, 3 suburban-area maps, and coverage map on verso. Notes, main legend, coverage/location maps, and image of building on cover.
